{"id": 2841, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得如今的互联网需要哪些宽容？", "description": "宽容和“不关我事”的区别在于，宽容愿意尝试去理解。", "record_count": 13593, "comment_count": 71, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190311173809rMVQxJU2P8LqYjlF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-14T17:00:22Z", "questions": [{"id": 5502, "title": "你觉得如今的互联网需要哪些宽容？", "content": "你觉得如今的互联网需要哪些宽容？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 332398, "content": "对“不知道”的宽容，闻道有先后，不知道也不是反智", "image": "img/option/option/20190311174144brkXU6VKZzdinDev.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332399, "content": "对“炫耀”的宽容，与其拆穿别人，不如保护他人的喜悦", "image": "img/option/option/20190311174247LzuxiYcDyI9mok8n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332400, "content": "对“直男审美”的宽容，不是谁都得追求所谓的“高级美”", "image": "img/option/option/20190311174410veBxXL6GDafhS9Rm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332401, "content": "对“脑残粉”的宽容，不影响他人，粉谁都是个人自由", "image": "img/option/option/20190311174637SKWyFkdGv7QE6LTY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332405, "content": "对“影视作品三观”的宽容，艺术和现实不是一回事", "image": "img/option/option/20190311174851eNGZC2it5qh06lsy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332409, "content": "对“政治不正确”的宽容，绝对思想统一无异于“正确暴力”", "image": "img/option/option/20190311175248vzLYMZWkrtlX6bQC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332411, "content": "对“名人私生活”的宽容，谁还没点道德瑕疵", "image": "img/option/option/20190311175419fZVjcTlr1oz0p2O3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 332415, "content": "对“不同观点”的宽容，不用啥都拒绝沟通地拉黑或杠", "image": "img/option/option/20190311181012L1T0KCusxrjZyI29.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}